OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fthickening to bring periods of rain,
OL,7,Fwith some heavier outbreaks late
OL,8,Fevening and during the early hours of
OL,9,FWednesday, before turning patchy
OL,10,Ftowards dawn. Southerly coastal winds
OL,11,Finitially fresh.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FTemperatures still up on
OL,14,Fseasonally averages, but significantly
OL,15,Fcooler than Tuesday. Rather cloudy
OL,16,Fmorning with some patchy light rain,
OL,17,Ffocused in the west. Mainly dry for
OL,18,Fafternoon with brighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
