OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,6,Fearly Thursday, clearing to frequent
OL,7,Fshowers for the afternoon. Friday wet
OL,8,Fand windy with best of shelter towards
OL,9,FInverness. Blustery showers Saturday,
OL,10,Fheavier and more frequent in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
